snippet.title: Jason Momoa Reveals Why Amber Heard Was Really Fired from Aquaman 2!
snippet.description:
Jason Momoa Reveals Why Amber Heard Was Really Fired from Aquaman 2! 

Amber heard has had a crazy year but it just keeps getting crazier!

Not only did she have a fallout with Johnny Depp, she was fired from many lead roles.

The thing is, the reason she was fired from Aquaman 2 is not what you think.

Watch the full video for the all the details!
